Package: libatomic-ops
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides implementations for atomic memory update operations
 libatomic_ops provides implementations for atomic memory update operations
 on a number of architectures.
 .
 This package provides the shared library libatomic_ops.

Package: libatomic-ops-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libatomic-ops (= ${binary:Version}), gcc-dev
Description: Development headers and libatomic-ops static library
 This package provides libatomic-ops.a, headers and pkgconfig data required
 to build applications, libraries or plugins using the libatomic-ops API.

